import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux';
import { logout } from '../features/actions';

const Home = () => {
  const user = useSelector((state) => state.user);
  const dispatch = useDispatch();

  const handleLogout = () => {
    dispatch(logout());
  };

  return (
    <Box sx={{ mt: 10, bgcolor: '#f5f5f5', py: 8 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
          {/* Welcome Section */}
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box
              sx={{
                p: 4,
                bgcolor: 'white',
                borderRadius: 2,
                boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
                display: 'flex',
                flexDirection: 'column',
                justifyContent: 'center',
                alignItems: 'center',
              }}
            >
              <Typography
                variant="h4"
                component="h1"
                gutterBottom
                sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333', textAlign: 'center' }}
              >
                Bienvenue au Tribunal de Commerce de Casablanca
              </Typography>
              <Typography
                variant="body1"
                color="text.secondary"
                paragraph
                sx={{ lineHeight: 1.6, textAlign: 'center' }}
              >
                Application moderne et réactive pour la gestion du Tribunal de Commerce de Casablanca. Facilitant
                l'accès aux services et informations.
              </Typography>

              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', mt: 2 }}>
                {user  || user.role || user.token  ? (
                  <Button
                    variant="contained"
                    color="error"
                    onClick={handleLogout}
                    sx={{
                      padding: '12px 24px',
                      borderRadius: '8px',
                      fontSize: '16px',
                      width: '200px',
                      textAlign: 'center',
                    }}
                  >
                    Se Déconnecter
                  </Button>
                ) : (
                  <Link to="/login" style={{ textDecoration: 'none' }}>
                    <Button
                      variant="contained"
                      color="primary"
                      sx={{
                        padding: '12px 24px',
                        borderRadius: '8px',
                        fontSize: '16px',
                        width: '200px',
                        textAlign: 'center',
                      }}
                    >
                      Se Connecter
                    </Button>
                  </Link>
                )}
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          {/* Features Section */}
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box
              sx={{
                p: 4,
                bgcolor: 'white',
                borderRadius: 2,
                boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
                display: 'flex',
                flexDirection: 'column',
                alignItems: 'flex-start',
                justifyContent: 'center',
              }}
            >
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333' }}>
                Fonctionnalités
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des utilisateurs
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des réservations
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des départements
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          {/* Benefits Section */}
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box
              sx={{
                p: 4,
                bgcolor: 'white',
                borderRadius: 2,
                boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
                display: 'flex',
                flexDirection: 'column',
                alignItems: 'flex-start',
                justifyContent: 'center',
              }}
            >
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333' }}>
                Avantages
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Facile à utiliser
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Conception réactive
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Sécurisé
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
